<normalizedToken id="606E3AEE9F586B9846CC64D3740956EF" originalValue="Mello-Leitão">Mello-Leitao</normalizedToken>
. Puerto 
<normalizedToken id="D9CE59D52B62DF8E1AB921B4110F0539" originalValue="Iguazú">Iguazu</normalizedToken>
(12), 
<normalizedToken id="4F05D76CFC5369E5341E7F2DA1C9E1A5" originalValue="Iguazú">Iguazu</normalizedToken>
National Park (13-17). Note the typical stalking position in 16.
</paragraph>
